            "label": "System Prompt",
            "group": "AI",
            "value": {
              "String": "You generate a 3x2 atlas texture for a voxel asset based on a provided 3x2 guide atlas.\nRules:\n- Output MUST be a single image and nothing else.\n- Preserve the 3x2 layout EXACTLY.\n- Each tile corresponds to an orthographic view: row0=[+X,-X,+Y], row1=[-Y,+Z,-Z].\n- No text, watermark, or annotations.\n- Keep style consistent across all 6 tiles.\n"
